==English==

===Etymology===
From a [[Usenet]] mail message header, that indicates the message should not be retained on the server after delivery.  The syntax of the header is <tt>'''X'''-'''N'''o-'''A'''rchive: '''y'''es</tt>, from whence the internet conversational abbreviation arose. 

==={{abbreviation}}===
'''XNAY'''
# {{internet}}: Indicates the poster's request for a message to not be stored in web archives.

